    <h1>SPF (Sender Policy Framework)</h1>
    <p class="description">A DNS TXT record that tells receiving mail servers <strong>exactly which IPs are allowed to send email from your domain</strong>. The first line of defence against spoofing and a prerequisite for Gmail and Yahoo's 2024+ bulk sender requirements.</p>
